        "variant": "success",
        "title": "Beyond Cost Savings",
        "body": "Auto-scaling handled Black Friday with zero intervention (previous year required all-hands-on-deck). Deployment frequency increased from 2/month to 30/month. Developer velocity improved due to instant preview deployments. Team morale improved—no more 3am pages for scaling issues."
